Our Team
Altfest Personal Wealth ManagementSM has a staff of smart and friendly professionals dedicated to making your financial life easier. Our Wealth Management Team serves you in the way that best addresses your own special circumstances, sensitivities and concerns. The Investment Research Team provides the insights and guidance for making the right investment decisions for our clients, and our Client Administration and Client Relations Teams ensure that you are comfortable and happy at Altfest.
We invite you to learn more about our team members, their experience and life outside the firm.






