Company Overview of L.J. Altfest & Co., Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
L.J. Altfest & Co., Inc. provides investment management and financial planning services. It offers services in the areas of investments, retirement, college planning, insurance, estate planning, individual stocks, mutual funds, bonds, and private investments. L.J. Altfest & Co., Inc. was formerly known as Altfest, Young Associates Inc. and changed its name to L.J. Altfest & Co., Inc. in 1985. The company was founded in 1983 and is based in New York, New York.


